1. *Brat* se nada da će završiti fakultet za dve godine. (My brother hopes to finish university in two years.)
2. *Braća* su bila zaljubljena u istu devojku. (The brothers were in love with the same girl.)
3. *Brate* li se često? (Do you often hang out?)
4. *Brate*li se deca sa ulicom? (Do the kids hang out with the neighborhood?)
5. *Brate* se sa svojim prijateljima svaki vikend. (He hangs out with his friends every weekend.)